PN,30801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FThe Government must "stand up" to the
OL,8,Ffood industry after decades of failure
OL,9,Fto tackle obesity that is costing the
OL,10,Fcountry tens of billions a year, MPs
OL,11,Fhave said.
OL,13,FAll outdoor advertising of junk food
OL,14,Fshould be banned and front-of-pack
OL,15,Flabelling should be mandatory to
OL,16,Ftackle England's obesity epidemic, the
OL,17,FHealth and Social Care Committee said.
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FIt said its proposals, which include
OL,8,Fmandatory reporting and targets for
OL,9,Fsupermarkets, backed up with
OL,10,Fpenalties, on the amount of healthy
OL,11,Ffood they sell, aimed to fix a food
OL,12,Fenvironment that pushes consumers
OL,13,Ftowards high fat, sugar and salt
OL,14,F(HFSS) products, which are typically
OL,15,Fcheaper than nutritious food.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FThe proposals include new planning
OL,8,Fpolicies to stop fast food outlets
OL,9,Fopening close to schools, and
OL,10,Fimprovements to the NHS's Healthy
OL,11,FStart cards, given to pregnant women
OL,12,Fand parents of young children to buy
OL,13,Ffruit and vegetables.
OL,15,FMPs challenged the Government to be
OL,16,F"more courageous" in the face of
OL,17,Findustry lobbying against
OL,18,Frestrictions, which had meant that
OL,19,Fattempts to tackle obesity through
OL,20,Ffood policy "have continually failed".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@QO]|D@MOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care Committee
OL,8,Fchairwoman Layla Moran said: "When we
OL,9,Fsay the 'food environment', we mean
OL,10,Fthe constant bombardment of promotions
OL,11,Fand adverts we see and hear in our
OL,12,Fdaily lives ` on our screens, on
OL,13,Fchildren's journeys home from school,
OL,14,Fas we set foot in shops and queue for
OL,15,Fthe checkout.
OL,17,F"The central message of this report is
OL,18,Fthat we need to tackle England's
OL,19,Fescalating obesity crisis through
OL,20,Fprevention.
OL,26,@pD@^OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"That means bearing down on
OL,8,Fenvironmental factors that push people
OL,9,Fto eat unhealthily, that coerce
OL,10,Fstruggling families to buy their
OL,11,Fchildren products that fill them up
OL,12,Fwithout nourishing them.
OL,14,F"That is why the Government's food
OL,15,Fpolicy needs an overhaul. Perversely,
OL,16,Fthe worst options are the cheapest
OL,17,Fwhile the healthiest are harder to
OL,18,Faccess.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"Attitudes of obesity being purely
OL,8,Fdown to the individual failings are
OL,9,Foutdated and deny the reality of those
OL,10,Fliving with obesity and excess weight
OL,11,Fin this country needs robust
OL,12,Fchallenge."
OL,14,FShe added: "We ask this Government to
OL,15,Fbe bold, not to fudge and delay food
OL,16,Frestrictions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@KO]vD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"While we acknowledge the costs of
OL,8,Fpolicy changes to the food industry,
OL,9,Fthese are marginal compared to the
OL,10,Fhuge costs of inaction on obesity to
OL,11,Fsociety, the economy and the health
OL,12,Fservice.
OL,14,F"The real cost is measured in how many
OL,15,Fpeople suffer preventable diseases
OL,16,Flinked to being overweight or
OL,17,Fmalnourished.
OL,19,F"The Government needs to dig deep and
OL,20,Fprioritise the long-term health of
OL,21,Fgenerations to come."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FIn 2024, 30% of adults in England were
OL,8,Fliving with obesity, a further 36%
OL,9,Fwere overweight, and 28% of children
OL,10,Faged 13 to 15 were overweight or
OL,11,Fobese, according to NHS England.
OL,13,FObesity costs the UK #74.3 billion per
OL,14,Fyear, including #11.4 billion to the
OL,15,FNHS, according to research by Frontier
OL,16,FEconomics cited by the Department of
OL,17,FHealth and Social Care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FBetween August 2024 and July 2025,
OL,8,Fnearly #680 million was spent on
OL,9,Fadvertising food and soft drinks
OL,10,Fthrough TV, radio and outdoors.
OL,12,FProducts such as sweets, chocolates
OL,13,Fand crisps accounted for 29% of that
OL,14,Fspending, while fruit and vegetables
OL,15,Faccounted for 3%, the committee's
OL,16,Freport said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FFood and Drink Federation chief
OL,8,Fscientific officer Kate Halliwell
OL,9,Fsaid: "It's good that the committee
OL,10,Facknowledged the progress
OL,11,Fmanufacturers are making to reduce
OL,12,Fsalt, sugar and calories in everyday
OL,13,Ffood, and to increase fibre.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"We appreciate their support too for a
OL,8,Fscheme to help smaller businesses
OL,9,Fchange recipes to make products
OL,10,Fhealthier. However, we agree that more
OL,11,Fstill needs to be done and so we
OL,12,Fsupport the committee's call for
OL,13,Fgovernment to bring forward plans to
OL,14,Fintroduce mandatory reporting of
OL,15,Fhealthier food sales.
OL,17,F"However, we don't agree that food and
OL,18,Fdrink manufacturers should be excluded
OL,19,Ffrom discussions on health policy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"Government needs advice from the
OL,8,Fpeople who make food to understand if
OL,9,Fnew policies are workable in practice.
OL,10,FThis expertise doesn't exist in
OL,11,Fgovernment departments."
OL,13,FAn Advertising Association spokesman
OL,14,Fsaid: "This report represents a
OL,15,Fsignificant missed opportunity to put
OL,16,Fforward policies which would bring
OL,17,Ftogether government, industry, and the
OL,18,Fthird sector to tackle this major
OL,19,Fpolicy issue.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784125122
OL,3,CGovernment must 'stand up to the food
OL,4,Cindustry' to tackle obesity epidemic `
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"Decades of research across multiple
OL,8,Facademic disciplines has repeatedly
OL,9,Fshown that advertising does not
OL,10,Fcontribute to long-term changes in
OL,11,Fobesity or BMI and that advertising
OL,12,Frestrictions do not improve the
OL,13,Fnation's health.
OL,15,F"The focus should be on addressing the
OL,16,Freal drivers of poor health including
OL,17,Finequality, affordability, and
OL,18,Faccessibility of healthy food."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
